    "translation":{"eng":"When Providence becomes favorable, I shall attain Śrī Rūpa Mañjarī’s lotus feet and behold them with these two eyes. The abundant sweet beauty of Śrī Rūpa Mañjarī’s lotus feet will shine like the moon upon the blue lotus of my heart, causing it to blossom in jubilation both day and night."}},{
